<span id="freeTextContainer13281432916996640786">A superb biography of Albert Einstein! Walter Isaacson paints here the portrait of this inescapable rebel genius whose private and public lives cannot be analyzed without each other.<br/>Rich illustrations, personal Einstein documents, unpublished information! Great sensitivity. Fascinating!</span>

