<span id="freeTextContainer15653181655684749726"><i> Einstein: His Life and Universe</i> is but a mere pinch of Einstein&apos;s theories mixed in with a modest helping of his life. The brevity was too my taste as I was only in the mood for a tiny taste of Einstein bio. Too much of the genuis&apos; theory is liable to give me brain-freeze, so this was perfect. And done just the way I like it, tight and to the point. </span>
